{
  "stem": "25598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So she used to have a table with a stand, with an umbrella, with whatever, in front of the stores, and used to sell.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's how she brought up the girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the girls all helped in, in supporting the house in one way or another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, my father's family was much more well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my grandmother was hoping that if my mother marries somebody who is rich, by those standards, she will help with the dowry for the other two girls, which also didn't turn out that way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the plan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And eventually, my, my grandmother also opened up a little store, a few years before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was doing a lot better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My Aunt Mila, the youngest, was always helping her in the store until she got married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my Aunt Sidi married [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somebody who used to come as a tourist to Vadra-Dorna, which is also called Dorna, by the way, for short.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they lived in Belz, which was in Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were very, very well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was madly in love with her, so he didn't expect any dowry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so she moved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then my Aunt Mila married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her husband's name was Uncle Armin-- I mean was Armin And he was from another part of Romania, from Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my grandmother was extremely concerned that she doesn't know en-- know enough about him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She doesn't know enough about his family background, and, and what is his financial situation, and all of that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So and she was against-- she was basically against this marriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he said that he will forego the dowry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my grandmother said that she doesn't want him to forego the dowry.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
